name: The Lovers
description: The Lovers card can be a welcoming sight to any seeker when it comes to love and relationships. The Lovers tarot card represents a wonderful sense of unity and balance, as well as complementary energies. This doesn't have to be limited to another person; it can also refer to a choice between love and work, love and family, love and friendship, or even love and your entire way of life. The implication is that in order to have this love, you may have to make a sacrifice.
